<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1035701>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Site near road between Cachiyacu and Hacienda Cascas, Región Junín, Perú, where two individuals of Phrynopus montium were found in September 2014. Photo by R. von May." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1035701/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1035703>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Lateral and ventral views of live individuals of Phrynopus montium, found in September 2014 near the type locality. A – B (MUSM 33259, SVL 26.3 mm), C – D (MUSM 33260, SVL 20.9 mm). Photos by R. von May." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1035703/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1035705>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Lateral view of head and ventral view of left hand of preserved individuals of Phrynopus montium. A – B (MUSM 33259), C – D (MUSM 33260). Photos by R. von May." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1035705/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

